Reasoning: The paper discusses the challenges of additive manufacturing and proposes a solution involving in situ monitoring, feedback control, and semantic layers. This involves aspects of machine learning, control systems, computer vision, and optimization, which are all relevant to several arXiv CS sub-categories. Specifically, cs.MS (Machine Learning), cs.RO (Robotics), and cs.CV (Computer Vision) are likely due to the focus on monitoring and control, while cs.SY (Systems and Control) and cs.LG (Learning) are also possible due to the emphasis on feedback control and machine learning.
